This product uses data from Companies House.

- UK company data is derived from the Companies House "Free Company Data Product",
  published as open data under the Open Government Licence v3.0. Contains public sector
  information licensed under the Open Government Licence v3.0.
  See https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/doc/open-government-licence/version/3/
- The real dataset (~5.6M companies) is built monthly from the official snapshot by CI and
  distributed as a GitHub Release artifact (see README); the version bundled in this
  repository is a small ILLUSTRATIVE sample and is not real Companies House data.

companieswise reports the official Companies House register snapshot (UK-wide). It is a
MONTHLY snapshot of the live register: company status is as of the dataset date, not
real-time, and dissolved companies are generally absent. It is not legal, financial,
KYC/AML, credit or other professional advice.
